{"tid":498219,"cid":21,"subCid":5,"title":"[古典] classical instrument x vocalise","createTime":"2017-12-13T14:58:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-08T05:12:43.000Z","uid":23170,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"84431c2de346277f4b0180371c1518598e39d125","tid":498219,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T14:58:55.000Z","msg":"歌劇又好似無乜人like咁，但係instrumental classical又好多人like, 唔知依個人聲當instrument嘅music大家又like唔like?<br />\n<br />\n我聽過其實都只係有兩首，兩首都係女高音，兩首都好考唱嘅呼吸技巧，因為有好多較長要一次過帶嘅段落。而第二首有兩個movements, andante 同 allegro, andante考抒情技巧，要特別唱得細膩同好考唱嘅對每段段落嘅演譯，allegro比較輕快，講求歌唱嘅靈活度同敏捷性。allegro除左有好多密集嘅staccati (跳音）亦好考唱者嘅音域，特別係最後嘅high F好多時都會被跳過。<br />\n<br />\n比較出名有Vocalise - Sergei Rachmaninoff<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/5ZIQ2pHaJ1I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F5ZIQ2pHaJ1I&d=ExiKVpC%2B7Y99Pjk%2F%2F6lHalzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=5f9a8713\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/5ZIQ2pHaJ1I</a><br />\n<br />\n另外比較少人識就有依首concerto for coloratura soprano and orchestra op.82 - Reinhold Gliere<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0-RxDoXCCBM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0-RxDoXCCBM&d=ExiKVpC%2B7Y99Pjk%2F%2F6lHalzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=b30c2e82\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0-RxDoXCCBM</a>"},{"pid":"bfff98381eaca75250abce96ca797a713b58d0cf","tid":498219,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T23:49:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a05152cd5485e24f5b894f5f6922deb33ae6d307","tid":498219,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T03:32:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c669068cba458fa6ae97ce02abd5333ba8599db","tid":498219,"uid":135115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T03:46:54.000Z","msg":"Vocalise好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/goo